{"tid":1852064,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"全民豬咀，黃絲勇武或成最後大贏家","createTime":"2020-01-30T09:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T19:03:46.000Z","uid":110969,"like":78,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"75be6cdabffec96988a7f07d4d4a414a4e038e17","tid":1852064,"uid":110969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:35:44.000Z","msg":"當市面無晒口罩賣，網上都訂唔到，手持口罩就有閪屌既時候<br />\n大部分勇武或者有出去做後排既和理非，我相信都有個豬咀旁身<br />\n係時候拎返出黎用，一個6200 加塊P100 綿己經屌打抗疫神裝N95<br />\n更加唔好講以前個個都追求既60926，我諗一個已經頂到一個月<br />\n到時成條街都豬咀，又可以令反蒙面法自己收皮，救返大部分手足<br />\n藍絲們見到個個都上豬咀，人有我有心態就自動成為勇武<br />\n到時人人勇武，成為最後大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n香港人加油<br />\n想話比買唔到罩好擔心既黃絲知，其實你地一早準備好呢場抗疫既超神裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45ac6a7415ac8d37c05e1aff4bd60a158d073a9","tid":1852064,"uid":110969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f27784f7d54af350c878a8b85879d83d8a81fd","tid":1852064,"uid":11698,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2302bfd2211e6c25a7c7588dc3aa00a1248b1691","tid":1852064,"uid":110509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d5f27784f7d54af350c878a8b85879d83d8a81fd","tid":1852064,"uid":11698,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:43:30.000Z","msg":"俾晒人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"269a6efdcf1d1e3422d976f1f597fcd012adff95"